   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Sixty-four ONE DIED FOR ALL Scripture: 2 Cor 5:14 The One is Jesus Jesus is God coming to be the Savior of mankind.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Since He is God incarnated, He is an unlimited person.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>In God s eyes, all who believe in Jesus are included in Jesus.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>So Jesus is not only an unlimited person, but One that includes all.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>All are sinners All the people in the world are sinners.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Every sinner that believes in the Lord Jesus is included in this all.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>One died for all Apparently Jesus died as one individual, yet actually He died for all.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>That is, He died for those He redeemed, for all those who believe in Him.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>The reason that the Lord s death could become effective for all who believe in Him is that He is one with them and they are joined unto Him.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>All died All refers to all those who are joined unto Christ Jesus.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Since He died, all have died in God s sight.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>It is best to use the example of a nation destroyed.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Since all died because of His death, all do not need to die again.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>How to share in Jesus death</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Develop this point.</S>
   </TEXT>
